      dt
        a(href='http://iclc.livecodenetwork.org/2015/') ICLC 2015: International Conference on Live Coding
      //
        
            <dd>Live Coding (即興でプログラミングして音楽や動画を生成するメディア芸術の表現手法)に関する国際会議。2016年は<a href="http://iclc.livecodenetwork.org/2016/">カナダ</a>で開催。</dd>
        
      dt
        a(href='http://liveprogramming.github.io/2013/') LIVE 2013: First International Workshop on Live Programming
        |  (Co-located w/ 
        a(href='http://2013.icse-conferences.org/')
          abbr(title='The International Conference on Software Engineering') ICSE
        |  2013)
      //
        
            <dd>Live Programming (プログラミング中、継続的にプログラムの振る舞いが更新され、フィードバックが返る開発環境)に関する国際ワークショップ。第2回は<a href="http://2016.ecoop.org/home"><abbr title="The European Conference on Object-Oriented Programming">ECOOP</abbr></a> 2016併催となり、<a href="http://2016.ecoop.org/track/LIVE-2016">ローマ</a>で開催。SIGPX発起人 加藤がProgram Committeeメンバー。</dd>
        
      dt
        a(href='http://2016.ecoop.org/track/PX-2016') PX/16: First Edition of the Programming Experience Workshop
        |  (Co-located w/ 
        a(href='http://2016.ecoop.org/home')
          abbr(title='The European Conference on Object-Oriented Programming') ECOOP
        |  2016)
      //
        
            <dd>Programming Experienceに関する国際ワークショップ。SIGPX発起人 増原がCo-chair、加藤がProgram Committeeメンバー。</dd>
        
      dt
        a(href='http://www.ppig.org/node/1000')
          abbr(title='Psychology of Programming Interest Group') PPIG
          |  2016 - 27th Annual Workshop
        |  (Co-located w/ 
        a(href='https://sites.google.com/site/vlhcc2016/')
          abbr(title='IEEE Symposium on Visual Languages and Human-Centric Computing') VL/HCC
        |  2016)
      //
        
            <dd>プログラミングとソフトウェア工学周辺で生じる心理学関連のトピックを扱う歴史の古いワークショップ。</dd>
        
      dt
        a(href='http://2017.programming-conference.org/track/px-2017') PX/17: Second Edition of the Programming Experience Workshop
        |  (Co-located w/ 
        a(href='http://2017.programming-conference.org/home')
          abbr(title='The International Conference on the Art, Science, and Engineering of Programming') <Programming>
        |  2017)
      //
        
            <dd>Programming Experienceに関する国際ワークショップの第2回。SIGPX発起人 増原がCo-chair。</dd>
        
    p
      a(href='http://research.microsoft.com/en-us/projects/touchdevelop/') Publication of the Microsoft Research TouchDevelop team
      |  might also be of your interest. You will see that no event directly deals with programming environments, and yet various venues overlap with the topic. If you find any other relevant conferences/events, 
      a#apply-mail(href='https://junkato.jp') please let me know
      | .

